Guests can opt to be preened and pampered in the hotel's hairdressing salon. The hotel also features many shops.

This apartment complex is centrally located in the tourist resort of Costa Teguise, just some 400 m from the beach and around 800 m from the town centre. It is just a short distance from shopping areas with boutiques, bars and restaurants

The complex comprises a total of 36 apartments.

The apartments all come with an integrated living room/ bedroom, a separate bedroom, an en suite bathroom, a direct dial telephone, a hire safe, and either a balcony or terrace.

name.content: NH Las Palmas Playa las Canteras

description.content: This delightful beach hotel enjoys a superb setting in Las Palmas on the island of Gran Canaria. Guests will find themselves a mere 20 metres from Las Canteras Beach and just 10 minutes from one of the largest shopping centres in the city. A bus stop lies a few metres away from the hotel, from where guests can enjoy ease of access to other areas of the city. The tourist bus Las Palmas Guagua also departs from this point, which offers guests the opportunity to explore the area's attractions. The Alfredo Kraus Auditorium convention centre is situated less than 5 km away. Guests are welcomed by comfortable accommodation, friendly service, warm hospitality and excellent facilities and amenities.

This delightful beach hotel is situated at the heart of the bustling tourist centre of Las Palmas. Guests will find themselves just a few minutes' walking distance from the golden sands of Las Canteras beach. Links to public transport networks are a mere 30 metres from the hotel. Guests will appreciate the comfortable, well-equipped accommodation options, leisure amenities and dining choices. Guests are invited to dream the days away by the pool, or to enjoy a refreshing swim after an energetic workout in the gym. The guest rooms are beautifully-appointed and offer travellers the ideal place in which to relax and unwind at the end of the day.

The BEST NEGRESCO COMPLEJO is a must for everyone looking to enjoy the sea, thanks to its stunning setting right on the beach front. Of particular note are the panoramic views of the swimming pool. It's407 rooms offer customers a functional and pleasant environment. It has everything parents need to rest and to entertain young children. The facilities are completed with 4 swimming pools in which to enjoy a cooling dip.

The Best Cambrils hotel is located in the area of Vilafortuny only 80m from the beach. Comfortable rooms with balcony, fully fitted bathroom with hairdryer, telephone, satellite TV, fridge, security door lock, heating, air conditioning and optional safety deposit box. Buffet style restaurant with show cooking, national and international cuisine, bar-cafeteria, TV lounge and a snack-bar at the swimming pool. It has outdoor swimming pool for adults and children, games room, children's area and kid's club as well as day and night entertainment program. Optional services: spa, gift shops, internet corner, fitness centre, massage, ping pong and billiard.

This welcoming city hotel is located in Algeciras. The tourist centre with numerous shopping opportunities, boutiques, restaurants, bars and a lively nightlife is around 200 m away. Links to the public transport network also lie within walking distance. The nearest beach is 2 km away.

This hotel has 160 rooms (of which 5 are suites) are spread over 10 floors. Guests may make use of the 24-hour reception desk, safe, a currency exchange facility and a lift. There is also a caf√© and an air-conditioned restaurant with an extra non-smoking room available for use. A public Internet terminal are additionally available for business guests. Guests arriving by car may use garage facilities (fee). Laundry services round off the facilities on offer.

The cosy rooms come with an en suite bathroom with hairdryer, a direct dial telephone (fee), a hire safe and central heating. The spacious rooms have views of the harbor.

The nearest golf course is 25 km away.

Overlooking the Aiguadol√ß marina, the eternal blue of the Mediterranean Sea and the Garraf natural park, the stylish hotel Meli√° Sitges enjoys a privileged location in the heart of the yachting harbour, opposite the La Marina and Balmins beaches. The historic centre of Sitges can be reached within a 10-minute stroll. The international airport of Barcelona is just 25 km away, while Barcelona's city centre is reachable within 30 minutes. 
The hotel in a contemporary design offers bright and spacious rooms boasting spectacular views. Features of the hotel include a fantastic 4,000 m2 convention centre with an auditorium with capacity for 1,380 guests, making it one of the leading convention hotels in Spain. After a long day of conferences or exploring the picturesque coast of Catalonia, guests can relax in the excellent spa and wellness centre with fully-equipped gym, sauna and Turkish bath.

These apartments are situated in the tourist centre of Puerto Rico, within easy reach of the beach and a wide variety of shops, cafes, bars and restaurants. The nightlife in the area has much to offer.

Boasting fantastic views over the sea, this modern hotel is excellently located in the popular seaside resort of Cascais. The centre of Cascais is easily reachable, the Serra de Sintra with its World Heritage Site, the largest casino in Europe at Estoril, the famous Guincho Beach and several high-class golf courses can be reached within a short drive. Lisbon International Airport is about 35 km away.

This hotel is beautifully located in a residential area in Lloret de Mar, just 300 metres away from the tourist centre. The beach and the promenade are just a short distance away. A host of shopping, dining and entertainment opportunities can be found nearby. Links to the public transport network are just 100 metres away. This charming hotel is ideal for family holidays or weekend getaways. The guest rooms offer a peaceful, relaxed setting in which to completely unwind. Guests can enjoy a refreshing swim in one of the hotel's pools. The cosy terrace offers a relaxed dining experience. Guests are sure to enjoy a memorable stay at this charming hotel.

This beach hotel is located in the famous holiday resort of Lloret de Mar. The hotel is located just 300 metres away from the town centre. Guests will find themselves just 100 metres away from an array of shops and entertainment options. This wonderful hotel lies just 500 metres away from the beach. Links to the public transport network can be found just a few steps away from the hotel. This wonderful hotel greets visitors with warm hospitality and excellent service. The guest rooms are beautifully appointed, and are fitted with modern amenities. Guests will be pleased by the many facilities and services that the hotel has to offer.

This luxurious hotel is located in a magnificent setting in the city centre of Platja d'Aro and a few metres from the white, sandy beach, where guests can enjoy a vibrant nightlife and shopping options, as well as a natural environment. Extraordinarily set in the heart of Costa Brava, the premises are around 5 km from the picturesque town of S'Agar√≥ and 7 km from San Feliu de Gu√≠xols. Guests can completely relax and have a wonderful stay at this hotel thanks to its beautifully decorated guest rooms and suites, all of them perfectly equipped with air-conditioning, a fully stocked minibar, a safe and a private bathroom with a separate shower and a bathtub. Families might appreciate the mini club and the swimming pool which are part of the facilities. Apart from tasting exquisite delicacies, visitors can celebrate all kinds of events, such as weddings or business meetings at the hotel.

This hotel, surrounded by a 1,500 m¬≤ garden area, boasts a convenient location in the centre of Blanes, a town and municipality in the region of Selva in Girona, Catalonia, Spain. It offers easy access to the touristic centre and to the public transport network. Guests will be able to find a variety of restaurants, bars and discos close to this charming establishment. It is also just a short walk to the beach and the lively promenade. Featuring a choice of different room types to suit all travellers' needs, it organizes a stunning entertainment programme for guest enjoyment during the summer.

This quality apart hotel, surrounded by beautiful gardens, is located in the tourist area of Cala Santandria and is approximately 300 m from the beach. Ciudadella can easily be reached by car or public transport since it is only 2.5km form the hotel. Within the areas guests will be able to find restaurants, caf√©s and shopping venues. The airport is around 46 km from the hotel. This is a perfect place for families with children who wish to enjoy the Mediterranean sun.

This superb hotel is located in the district of San Antonio overlooking Taoro Park and just a 10 minutes' walk from the town centre of Puerto de la Cruz. The hotel is just 800 metres from the nearest beach and enjoys close proximity to the Lido Marti√°nez, charming restaurants, casino and entertainment parks. Enjoying its idyllic, sheltered setting at the foot of the famous Orotava Valley, the hotel is the ideal choice for travellers looking for a relaxing holiday close to the beach yet still at the heart of the action. The hotel greets guests with a warm, serene environment, exemplary service and attention to detail. Guests will be impressed by the hotel's stylishly-decorated rooms, conference spaces, leisure options and entertainment programme, as there is something to tempt every type of traveller.

This charming hotel enjoys a superb location in the centre of Barcelona. Within walking distance, guests will be able to reach a number of touristic sites of historic and cultural interest, such as Plaza Catalu√±a, Passeig de Gr√†cia and La Pedrera. The hotel is also within walking distance of convenient public transport links and very close to the most vibrant shopping area of the city. This is definitely a perfect place from where to start discovering this wonderful city.

Situated just off Pla√ßa de Catalunya and Las Ramblas, this elegant, contemporary style hotel with its beautiful modernist entrance is located in the heart of the Catalan capital. A large variety of exclusive boutiques, shops, restaurants, bars and caf√©s is in the vicinity, Passeig de Gr√†cia, Gaud√≠'s Casa Batll√≥, the old town Barri G√≤tic or the art nouveau concert hall Palau de la M√∫sica are within a short stroll.

This beach hotel is situated on a main road in the lively centre of Arenal and is approximately 500 m from the local and renowned sandy beach. Within the area guests will be able to find public transport links, which provide access to most important touristic and historic points of the island. This hotel is ideal for those guests who wish to spend their holidays under the bright Mediterranean sun.

Summer is synonymous with laughing, beach and freedom. That is why at FERGUS G√©minis we bet for a different accommodation, full of leisure plans and spaces specially designed for your entertainment and comfort. Everything located a few metres away from Arenal beach, at the heart of Palma's bay.

Located near S'Arenal yacht club, this is one of our reference hotels in Majorca for travellers who, like you, want to make the most of their holidays in Majorca. It is ideal for your trips with friends or family, as it will allow you to relax and enjoy without worries.

Swimming pools, solarium terraces, varied buffet restaurant, indoor bar, snack bar, free wifi area, bike parking with repairing station and bike shower and recently refurbished superior rooms. Discover all the services the FERGUS G√©minis invites you to enjoy during your holidays.

Apart from modern and adapted facilities and a personalized attention, at our hotel in Arenal you will have everything you need for an unforgettable holiday.

Relax admiring one of the best sunsets of Majorca, resting in your room near the beach, savouring a delicious cocktail or having a walk along the seaside promenade‚Ä¶ And live unique experiences enjoying long cyclotouristic routes, excursions to the mountain, sunny days near the sea or a family adventure in the water parks of the island.

Surrounded by a beautiful green environment with artificial lakes, waterfalls and a lush vegetation, this appealing vacation resort is an ideal spot to spend a pleasant family holiday or a romantic retreat for couples. The complex is located in a peaceful area of Golf del Sur, making it a great option for golf lovers, while the beach is some 100 m away. The immediate vicinity offers a big shopping centre with a variety of restaurants, caf√©s, bars and shops. The accommodation units are especially designed with guests' comfort in mind and feature a separate bedroom, a fully-equipped open kitchen area and a living room. Some of the apartments also have a private balcony overlooking the large outdoor pool. Guests can taste local specialities in the on-site restaurant, while the poolside bar invites travellers to relax and enjoy a refreshing drink or a light snack. The resort offers daily activities for adults and children alike, including a kids club, a massage service and a separate pool for the little ones.Lunch and Breakfast are served at Grand Muthu Golf Plaza Hotel.

This city hotel is situated in the historic centre of Porto. The hotel is located close to the treasure trove of attractions the city has to offer including Palacio da Bolsa, the Portwine Institute and the San Francisco Church. Close by, guests will find an array of shopping venues, lively bars and charming restaurants. Guests are welcomed by an air of calm and tranquility, in which to enjoy a relaxing break away from the bustle of daily life. The hotel offers comfortable surroundings, warm hospitality, excellent service and facilities to ensure that guests enjoy all the comforts and convenience possible for a truly enjoyable city getaway.

description.content:
This hotel is located in the tourist centre of Roquetas de Mar, just 500 metres from the long sandy beach. Numerous shops as well as restaurants, bars and public transport are in the hotel's immediate vicinity.

Opened in 1990, this 3-storey hotel consists of a total of 149 double rooms. The lobby contains a reception offering 24-hour service, a currency exchange and a lift. Additional facilities include a caf√©, a bar and a restaurant. There are also laundry services available.

The snug en suite rooms contain a hairdryer, a direct dial telephone, satellite/ cable TV, a fridge, central heating and a hire safe.

In the outdoor complex there is a pool, a snack bar as well as a sun terrace with sun loungers and parasols. Sports enthusiasts may enjoy the aerobics, a game of snooker, minigolf as well as the various water sports available nearby. The nearest golf course is just 800 m from the hotel.

Guests may choose their breakfast, lunch or evening meals from individual buffets.
The on-site facilities include tennis courts, hairdressers, gymnasium, saunas, hot tub and beautician. Also on site there is a restaurant and swimming pool.

This superb hotel enjoys a strategic setting in one of the most exclusive commercial areas of Seville. Situated in the city centre, this sublimely located hotel is just 15 minutes from the Santa Cruz district, where guests can explore the cathedral and the Giralda. The hotel is a mere 400 metres from Santa Justa train station, from where guests can enjoy ease of access to the city, while the nearest metro station is just 200 metres away. The airport is just a 10 minutes' drive away. Hailed as one of the biggest in Seville and the first in Spain to obtain a quality assurance certificate from AENOR, this superb hotel offers guests impeccable service and exemplary attention to detail, sure to surpass the expectations of even the most discerning travellers. Guests are invited to wine and dine in style in one of the hotel's excellent dining choices, there is something to tempt every palate.

This city hotel is located in the renowned Barri Gotic of Barcelona, right in the centre of the city and close to Las Ramblas and other places of touristic and cultural interest. Within the area, guests will be able to find a wide range of cafes, restaurants, boutiques and shopping centres, as well as bars, pubs and discos, suitable to all tastes. Public transport services are also reachable within a two minute walk. This is a perfect hotel for those friends or couples wishing to experience Barcelona's vibrant atmosphere.

This city hotel is located above Puerto de la Cruz in the San Antonio district of the town, this hotel offers guests the best of both worlds. Sitting just 2 kms from the town centre and the beach, the hotel provides guests with ease of access to the vibrant tourist hub of the town, and the relaxing environment of the beach. The hotel is also just 100 metres from links to the public transport system, placing many attractions within easy reach. Guests will be pleased with the warm hospitality and inviting environment that will greet them. The hotel offers a relaxing pool area where travellers can lie back and unwind or enjoy a refreshing swim. The hotel also provides dining options for guests convenience and comfort.

This hotel is located in the tourist area of Arcos de la Frontera (Cadiz) and only 500 m away from the centre with bars, restaurants, caf√© and boutiques.

This hotel comprises a total of 44 rooms spread over 4 floors. Further facilities include a bar, a reception desk and an air-conditioned √† la carte restaurant. Laundry services and room service are also on offer within the hotel. A car park and a garage round up the facilities on offer.

The tasteful rooms come with a bathroom, a direct dial telephone, a hire safe and central heating.

The hotel offers its guests use of a sun terrace in the well-tended outdoor complex.

Guests may select their breakfast from an ample buffet.

This pleasant hotel is situated close to the famous nature and wildlife reserves of Sierra de Cazorla and Segura y Las Villas. Featuring a rooftop Japanese Garden with a swimming pool, which treats to great views of Baeza, the venue blends a historical 19th-century building with contemporary minimalist design and an artistic vibe. Mixing fine wooden floors, metallic details, stone bathrooms and contemporary furniture, the interior of all the rooms and suites makes them unique, but not at the expense of comfort or convenience. Guests can relax with a refreshing beverage at the onsite cafe or when the weather permits in the Japanese garden. The can start their day with a buffet breakfast consisting of fresh, local produce served in the charming roof garden.

This hotel is situated in Palma del Rio, just 1 km away from the resort centre. Cordoba is just 54 km away. Many boutiques, cafes, bars, restaurants and nightclubs can be found close by. Links to the public transport network can be found just a short walking distance away. Seville Airport is 70 km away. This hotel is set amidst 2000 metres squared of gardens, around a 17th-century courtyard. The guest rooms come well equipped with modern amenities, for visitors' convenience. The hotel features a conference room, for business travellers. Guests will appreciate the delectable dining experience that the hotel's restaurant has to offer. Guests can sit back and unwind with a refreshing drink from the bar.
